      "content": "exactly. and it feels like whenever people try to point that out, they get labeled as \"bigots\" or something just to shut them up. so if the whole point of the movement is equality, why does it feel like it's actually creating a new kind of intolerance where you can't even question things anymore? isn't that just the opposite of what social justice is supposed to be?",
